```go
import "fmt" 

func main() {  
  var a string 
Start:  
  for {  
    switch {  
    case a < "aaa":  
      goto A  
    case a >= "aaa" && a < "aaabbb":  
      goto B  
    case a == "aaabbb":  
      break Start  
    }  
  A:  
    a += "a"  
    continue Start  
  B:  
    a += "b"  
    continue Start  
  }  
fmt.Println(a) 
} 

```
